This is just a random text editor i felt like making. We'll see if we finish it. :D

You need ncurses to run this. I can't remember if you need to install it in some way, but i just thought it would be useful to know.

The Makefile uses g++, so you will need that aswell.

Current tasks are in the TODO file.

When i say basic, i mean basic. All you can do is open a file, edit text, save the file (CTRL + S), and exit (CTRL + X).
